REQUIREMENTS

 - pluma >=2.15.2
 - Python >=2.6
 - PyGTK >=2.12
 - GTK+ >=2.10.14
 - PyEnchant (optional, needed for LaTeX spell checking)
 - Poppler Python Bindings (optional, needed for embedded PDF preview)

INSTALLATION

Just copy the contents of the archive (folder 'PlumaLaTeXPlugin' and file
'PlumaLaTeXPlugin.pluma-plugin') to '~/.config/pluma/plugins' where '~'
is your home directory. You may have to create the folder 'plugins'.

Restart pluma and activate the plugin in the plugins configuration.
